Class SupertypeList

java.lang.Object
org.microbean.assign.SupertypeList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<TypeMirror>, Collection<TypeMirror>, List<TypeMirror>, SequencedCollection<TypeMirror>
public final class SupertypeList extends Object implements List<TypeMirror>
An immutable List of TypeMirrors sorted in a specific way, intended to store the supertypes of a TypeMirror.
Author:
Laird Nelson
See Also:
  • Types.supertypes(TypeMirror)
